ical area where suitable habitats are threatened by changes in land use and periodic droughts.",Chambers et al. (2009) | Hafner & Geluso (1983) | Hafner | Timm & Lacher (2008a) | Jolley et al. (2000) | Patton (2005b) | Williams | S.L. (1999a) | Williams | S.L. & Baker (1974),
