lagus cuniculus ). Recommendations are to enforce existing laws prohibiting hunting and trade of Hainan Hares, improve habitat management, and enhance education at local, national, and international levels about their protected status.",Flux & Angermann (1990) | Hoffmann & Smith (2005) | Kong Lingming et al. (2016) | Lazell et al. (1995 | 2008) | Smith (2008c),
