ell (2009) | Mitchell & Hattingh (1993) | Mitchell & Skinner (1993 | 2003 | 2004 | 2009) | Mitchell | Bobbitt & Devries (2008) | Mitchell | Maloney et al. (2006) | Mitchell | van Schalkwyk & Skinner (2005) | Mitchell | van Sittert & Skinner (2009a | 2009b) | Pellew (1983a | 1983b | 1984a | 1984b) | Pienaar (1969) | Pilgrim (1911) | Pratt & Anderson (1982) | Ridewood (1904) | Robin et al. (1960) | Scheepers (1992) | Shortridge (1934) | Simmons & Scheepers (1996) | Singer & Boné (1960) | Skinner & Chimimba (2005) | Skinner & Hall-Martin (1975) Skinner & Smithers (1990) | Solounias (1999) | Spinage (1968 | 1993) | Van Aarde (1976) | Van Sittert et al. (2010) | Van Schalkwyk et al. (2004) | Von Linnaeus (1758) | Wyatt (1971) | Young & Okello (1998),
