 Least Concern on The IUCNRed List. Wagner's Common Mustached Batis one of the most common insectivorous bats in Amazon lowlands.,Appel et al. (2017) | Bernard (2002) | Bernard et al. (2011) | Bowles et al. (1979) | Bredt et al. (1999) | Clare et al. (2013) | Filippi-Codaccioni et al. (2018) | Ibanez & Ochoa (1989) | Lima et al. (2017) | Lépez-Baucells | Torrent et al. (2018) | Oliveira et al. (2015) | Pavan & Marroig (2016) | Pavan et al. (2018) | Sampaio et al. (2003) | Smith (1972) | de Thoisy et al. (2014),https://zenodo.org/record/6419843/files/figure.png
