ergrazing by livestock threatens grasslands. It is not clear if the northern subspecies, macrocephalus , persists.",Corti & Lavrenchenko (2008) | Lopez-Antonanzas & Wesselman (2013) | Monadjem et al. (2015) | Sillero-Zubiri et al. (1995a) | Yalden (1985 | 2013a) | Yalden & Largen (1992),
