urnal.",,"Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Additional ecological studies of Vieira’s Tree-rat, a rare Amazonian endemic, are needed.",lack-Ximenes et al. (2005) | Patton et al. (2015),https://zenodo.org/record/6623866/files/figure.png
